text: Brooke Hogan (born May 5, 1988 in Tampa, Florida) is an American singer, actress and model who currently has her own show on VH1 and MuchMore called Brooke Knows Best it is a spin-off of the show her parents were on called Hogan Knows Best. Her father is semi-retired professional wrestler Hulk Hogan. She released her debut album in 2006 entitled Undiscovered. == Other websites == * Category:1988 births Category:Living people Category:Actors from Tampa, Florida Category:American movie actors Category:Models from Florida Category:Professional wrestling authority figures Category:Singers from Tampa, Florida
